<span id="Description"></span>
==Описание==

The '''Std TileWindows''' command rearranges the windows in the [[Main_view_area|Main view area]] so that they are all visible and do not overlap. The result is determined by the order in which the windows were last activated.

[[Image:Std_TileWindows_example.png|400px]]
{{Caption|Main view area with three tiled windows}}

<span id="Usage"></span>
==Применение==

# The Main view area must contain at least two windows.
# Select the {{MenuCommand|Windows → [[Image:Std_TileWindows.svg|16px]] Tile}} option from the menu.


